Updated Algorithm for Quiz Player:

1. Import libraries that will be needed.
2. Allow users to choose between the two options (Play a Quiz, View History, Exit).
3. If users choose Play a Quiz:
    3.1. Allow users to choose from the present quiz category.
    3.2. Allow users to input their name.
    3.3. Allow users to answer the quiz.
    3.4. Print the result and save to Data Information file.
4. If users choose View History.
    4.1. Allow users to choose from the available names.
    4.2. View the category, score, date, and average of the users in a certain quiz.
5. If users choose exit they will be able to exit to the program.